SubjectOrder Designating the Department of Health and the Department of Citizenship and Immigration to provide support to the Minister of Border Security and Organized Crime Reduction
PrecisOrder Designating (1) the Department of Health to provide support to the Minister of Border Security and Organized Crime Reduction in the carrying out of his or her responsibilities relating to cannabis; and (2) the Department of Citizenship and Immigration to provide support to the Minister of Border Security and Organized Crime Reduction in the carrying out of his or her responsibilities relating to border security.
